on the note of top endpoints, stuff like avatar.roblox.com isn't necessarily spread across (well I guess technically) 200+ endpoints, the ID changes, so it'd be nice to have it say `/v2/avatar/users/<USER_ID>>/outfits` instead of listing out every ID. But if you click it, it will give a list of IDs for more info, and this should apply in general (like servers/votes for `games.roblox.com/v1/...`)
